%%{ init: { 'theme': 'default' } }%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant AuthServer
    participant ResourceServer

    User->>AuthServer: Login with credentials
    AuthServer-->>User: JWT token + Refresh token

    User->>ResourceServer: Access protected resource with JWT token
    ResourceServer-->>AuthServer: Validate JWT token
    AuthServer-->>ResourceServer: Token valid
    ResourceServer-->>User: Access granted

    User->>AuthServer: Request new access token with Refresh token
    AuthServer-->>User: New JWT token (if refresh token is valid)